data.description: Feel like you moving in to a new construction. This gorgeous home has quartz in kitchen and laundry room area.  Open floor plan and over 2 acres 100% uplands. The master bedroom has a wide walk in shower from both sides and double closets. COME AND CHECK OUT ALL THE UPGRADES THIS HOMES COMES WITH. Beautiful street and a lot of backyard space to add a pool.
